{"tid":1947582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"與女警密切接觸的8名警員中5人初步檢測呈陰性 另2名抽血員呈陰性","createTime":"2020-03-28T11:26:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T02:14:13.000Z","uid":21470,"like":5,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"de85c8301fa0301332266e0691f6b166dd487d9d","tid":1947582,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T11:26:31.000Z","msg":"警方指確診女警8名密切接觸者5人初步結果呈陰性<br />\n<br />\n警方指，8名駐守深水埗分區的警務人員，界定為22歲確診女警的密切接觸者，當中5人的初步病毒檢測結果呈陰性，其餘3人正等候檢測。他們全部要入住檢疫中心，當中2人昨日已入住火炭駿洋邨，其餘6人今日入住駿洋邨及鯉魚門度假村。另外，一名曾經與確診女警接觸的槍械訓練科人員，未有界定為密切接觸者，但已接受測試，正等候結果，警方已安排她暫停槍械訓練工作，減少與他人接觸。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局指，早前為女警抽血的兩名抽血員，測試對病毒呈陰性反應，兩人陸續獲安排到隔離營接受檢疫隔離。醫管局再度呼籲市民聽從醫護人員指示，在醫院內需要佩戴口罩。這名女警日前確診，她在明愛醫院期間未有戴口罩，兩名為她抽血、進行靜脈注射及做心電圖的抽血員，被列為密切接觸者，要隔離檢疫。警方表示深感抱歉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1277102&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1277102%26csid%3D261_341&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOq258GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=7af3e903\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1277102&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"fc05ee03e5136d9ba6542b845e2e5bc9a5c3e43c","tid":1947582,"uid":309935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T11:28:54.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"0d0e7c3ec7eee6f160fceeaaa40732bec4400955","tid":1947582,"uid":221171,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T11:29:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CeSwrxB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCeSwrxB.png&h=48a439d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S34F4ji.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS34F4ji.gif&h=93961608&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NioWCEj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNioWCEj.jpg&h=fd1abb59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gSf2ycF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgSf2ycF.jpg&h=3fc729e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4CK3hEq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4CK3hEq.gif&h=48e7ae7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d5f629a3379aacd277c4c86bc41f9660042fab1","tid":1947582,"uid":126621,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T11:30:02.000Z","msg":"最好結果係假陰性<br />\n返狗屋繼續傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9056d1eb1f128b963d58353792e4c1be45272e0c","tid":1947582,"uid":235015,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T11:30:13.000Z","msg":"警方指<br />\n<br />\n同埋過得兩三日咋，分分鐘仲潛伏期緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c918695f7d5a016ace3dbe68cb98ce626c59e8b0","tid":1947582,"uid":282362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T11:30:17.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"f45ab90125575e3552c7d3a56c3817cbcc22f826","tid":1947582,"uid":302236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T11:35:10.000Z","msg":"手足可唔可以幫我推下po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府新措施 文宣新方向<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1946045\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1946045</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"194208e230d437a24a5ca0fdcdb78c9408b1ce14","tid":1947582,"uid":37722,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9056d1eb1f128b963d58353792e4c1be45272e0c","tid":1947582,"uid":235015,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T11:30:13.000Z","msg":"警方指<br />\n<br />\n同埋過得兩三日咋，分分鐘仲潛伏期緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T11:36:35.000Z","msg":"唔會因爲潛伏期就呈陰性架<br />\n<br />\n唉屌天無眼 手足就比人打到仆街 黑警就病痛都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/